    'from' => 'Phillip McGregor',
    'body' => 'On Thu, 4 Dec 1997 14:11:52 -0500, you wrote:

>Date: Thu, 4 Dec 1997 10:42:08 EST
>From: SemoFetus <SemoFetus@aol.com>
>Subject: Re: FF&S-TNE and presentation (was Re: Virus--This...)
